        {
            "id": 6009740,
            "title": "傑昇通信：報稅季荷包縮水 618檔期消費者趨理性",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>迎戰 618 年中購物檔期，手機通路業者觀察到今年消費行為出現明顯變化。傑昇通信指出，今年 618 檔期適逢報稅季，不少民眾荷包稍顯緊縮，消費更趨理性，高效降價與免萬元入手成為刺激買氣的兩大主軸。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009740%2Fl%2Fa3f6d36c66e0167a8e308a754fd8cd11.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009740%2Fl%2Fa3f6d36c66e0167a8e308a754fd8cd11.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009740%2Fl%2Fa3f6d36c66e0167a8e308a754fd8cd11.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009740%2Fl%2Fa3f6d36c66e0167a8e308a754fd8cd11.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009740%2Fl%2Fa3f6d36c66e0167a8e308a754fd8cd11.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009740%2Fl%2Fa3f6d36c66e0167a8e308a754fd8cd11.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009740%2Fl%2Fa3f6d36c66e0167a8e308a754fd8cd11.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009740%2Fl%2Fa3f6d36c66e0167a8e308a754fd8cd11.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009740%2Fl%2Fa3f6d36c66e0167a8e308a754fd8cd11.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009740%2Fl%2Fa3f6d36c66e0167a8e308a754fd8cd11.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009740%2Fl%2Fa3f6d36c66e0167a8e308a754fd8cd11.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009740%2Fl%2Fa3f6d36c66e0167a8e308a754fd8cd11.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009740%2Fl%2Fa3f6d36c66e0167a8e308a754fd8cd11.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009740%2Fl%2Fa3f6d36c66e0167a8e308a754fd8cd11.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009740%2Fl%2Fa3f6d36c66e0167a8e308a754fd8cd11.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009740%2Fl%2Fa3f6d36c66e0167a8e308a754fd8cd11.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009740%2Fl%2Fa3f6d36c66e0167a8e308a754fd8cd11.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">傑昇通信：適逢報稅季荷包縮水 618檔期消費者趨理性。(圖：傑昇通信提供)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>財政部因應美國實施「對等關稅」政策對台灣經濟造成衝擊，已發布延長 113 年度所得稅結算申報及繳納期間至 6 月 30 日的措施。在此背景下，手機通路業者觀察到消費者購機行為更加務實，對價格敏感度明顯提升。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>次促銷活動涵蓋蘋果、三星、OPPO、小米、vivo 等主要品牌，精選機種最高現省破萬元，折扣低至 62 折。其中三星 Galaxy S25 Ultra 從 47900 元降至 37690 元，現省 10210 元，成為降價幅度最大的旗艦機種。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>中階與平價機種同樣推出大幅折扣，OPPO Reno13 F 從 12990 元降至 8090 元，打出 62 折優惠。vivo Y39 特價 6890 元，換算相當於 63 折，滿足小資族與長輩族群的換機需求。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>傑昇通信表示，門市購機專屬優惠折扣甚至比網路價格更低，透過實體通路優勢吸引消費者。業者預期透過大幅降價策略，在消費緊縮的環境下維持競爭力，同時刺激 618 檔期的整體買氣。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><figure><img data-height=\"567\" data-mime=\"image/jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.3403880070546736\" data-src-m=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/6009740/m/323f2609f67813d7f2d48c7b38d532a6.jpg\" data-width=\"760\" src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/6009740/l/323f2609f67813d7f2d48c7b38d532a6.jpg\"/></figure></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p> </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
